{"tid":1679422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男子涉藏汽油彈　申請保釋獲批","createTime":"2019-10-28T07:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:31:39.000Z","uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2605dadbf1430c157c39c813c1a7358ae8f7a3f6","tid":1679422,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:58:36.000Z","msg":"兩名男子涉嫌於本月13日在荃灣華都中心藏有汽油彈、剪刀及打火機燃料等物品，各被控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。兩人早前在沙田裁判法院提堂，被拒絕保釋外出，兩人今日到高等法院申請保釋獲批，案件在將於12月10日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n報稱是大學生的20歲被告，被控無合法權限或辯解在公眾地方攜有攻擊性武器，即兩支汽油彈、4個打火機、一把剪刀及錘子。他獲准以港幣2萬元保釋外出，外加父親人事擔保金10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n另一名26歲被告報稱是見習工程師，同樣被控無合法權限或辯解在公眾地方攜有攻擊性武器，即一支汽油彈、一個丫叉、一些金屬珠、一個打火機及一把剪刀。他獲准港幣10萬元保釋外出，外加堂兄人事擔保金10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n兩人的保釋條件亦包括不得離開香港，並交出所有旅遊證件、到警署報到、遵守晚上10時至翌日早上六6時的宵禁令，並需居住於報稱地址。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪俾幾隻臥底狗禁底左....<br />\n其他街坊淨拍片唔出手組隊打波果次????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966e7ffb6a0e70a0a7f97aa0751a4a7985136dc9","tid":1679422,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fe6d1dfd35b1f4a10f6d109ea61dd3ee49ae09f5","tid":1679422,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10月31星期四：太子靈堂悼念太子站事件兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />11月2星期六：維園集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ayU5dBt.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/wQNKuag.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"c726b2c03d9de8ec51d288031cfd19807847674a","tid":1679422,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"上次個藍絲的士佬全車彈<br />\n之後點"},{"pid":"8ec4396b78bfc40c9af63f61722ec7d2a895fe45","tid":1679422,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD56zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=8eeee9ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"6531eae24f7cd69edb3bd0feadfef499cbe39cd8","tid":1679422,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"插贜"},{"pid":"b2e1a522218b9e98920019dd14fa33e4f5c3a60d","tid":1679422,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c726b2c03d9de8ec51d288031cfd19807847674a","tid":1679422,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"上次個藍絲的士佬全車彈<br />\n之後點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/車廂涉藏汽油彈-松節水等-兩男被控管有攻擊性武器等罪-一人不獲保釋/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E6%B6%89%E8%97%8F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%9D%BE%E7%AF%80%E6%B0%B4%E7%AD%89-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7